Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:20.06,mianze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(160,500)}翻譯:娜娜莉  校譯:小呆 時間&特效:幽幽子 打雜:面麻醬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙 燙燙燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「請吃吧」還得意洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 我忽然覺得好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 感覺怪難受的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波個頭最大 那就給你最大的那個 給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「波波個頭最大」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經長這麼壯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 太好吃了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢 給我最怎樣的呢 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給雪集的是葡萄乾最多的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 我希望你能直接告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 紙 紙 還有筆 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個寫出面麻的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 寫不出來啊仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 明明都寫在日記本上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨水還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再試一次 給我 我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子 好難受 鶴…子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 現在好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 感覺全身無力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 沒有生我們的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經原諒我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有原諒我們 我們無從知道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她還生氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡還會給我們做什麼蒸麵包…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許正是因為她還沒有原諒我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了責備我們 才出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種可能也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能寫字的話 一開始就寫出來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有道理 那樣的話我們也能交流 也能立刻相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為仁碳和面麻 都挺笨的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 說什麼要相信面麻的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果不還是自己獨佔了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城 存好打工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花 我們要做給她看 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要 讓面麻成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折騰得那麼厲害 也難怪會累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家打算要做煙花 為了讓你…成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子…就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 跑太快的話危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法原諒…原諒喜歡仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…果然還是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有放棄…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的輪班 能不能和我換一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪班？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週四 橋那邊有個工程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日薪挺高的 所以週四想去那裡打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算玩膩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:49.68,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個啊 那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是她... 芽衣子的母親和山先生聯繫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 叔叔您 並不反對煙花的事情對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活在過去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子變成那樣之後 她的時間就停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她拉回到現實中來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我不想讓她再回憶起來更多了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨的想法可能有些可笑 但我覺得我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 喜歡您的女兒 喜歡芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了芽衣子 我想做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也還活在過去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然會做出這麼沒面子的事情 真讓我驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一點沒變啊 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了面麻的話什麼都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信的話就可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓面麻成佛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼地在意面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明通過宿海就可以和她交談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過宿海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 接下來要去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為今晚也會幹到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在這之前 先把面麻送回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼 不想總憋在屋裡 我去哪兒都要跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 想和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 她說「想和大家一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 還是留著長髮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯 說起來她和我們一樣也在成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成長…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰會喜歡她這醜女…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 一般般…漂亮… 還是該說是可愛型的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是一般般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你個呆子 笨蛋 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一般般啦 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得像是在演獨角戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 並不是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.77,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9話「大家和面麻」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花 煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了 cool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過火藥必須由我來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的地方 你們試著幫幫忙如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這太嚇人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個會從竹筒裡出來對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色多點的話 看起來比較可愛 感覺應該會不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？ 你還真是和給人的形象不一樣呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 在這裡點火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 那麼這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那裡只是裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了抬上發射台的時候方便點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.23,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面麻 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放手啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她跑你背上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 面麻 你饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:56.23,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波波波 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 明明看不到 卻又能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比不過她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是 現在也是 一直比不過她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去買點果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛才也差點就喊出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻還在我們身邊 我認同了這點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卻看不到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連交談也辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再見面麻一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼只有宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對宿海也是 果然還是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個時候一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還叫著仁碳 一下就換成宿海了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嗎 你那一幅已經看透別人心思的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看透的也就只有你 是相似的人之間產生的共鳴之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你這種性格惡劣的人相似 絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我說過的那件事 那個事 我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆要不要試著交往一下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是對男孩子沒有抵抗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的中段踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 什麼漂亮的中段踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笑的時候啊 我真的嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼令你吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 燃起幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 安鳴的布偶不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 突然間就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是反覆無常的小貓咪啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果啊 如果面麻真的在仁碳那的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望實現了以後面麻不就消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到該打工的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就要去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 面麻你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和波波一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想留在這裡 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 當然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎歡迎 熱烈歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬧得太凶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興…啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.44,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 那個 我看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 我還以為是夏天的猛獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在都已經是穿冬裝的季節了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.29,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香港 與殭屍戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 寫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.26,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 你太厲害了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是在家的本子上卻寫不上 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多寫點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說點什麼吧 多多益善
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…你對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 對了 玩接龍嗎 畫畫接龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼啊 好像金楚糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙帶背包 紅寶石…石…玻璃球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗歐…歐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手上的紋和紋對起來就是 幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡 面麻隊員開始進行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:14.83,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您撥打的號碼現在不在服務區或已經關機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 打不通 還在打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要走得這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她應該 在秘密基地那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼 這麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 面麻消失什麼的 絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對絕對不要讓仁碳死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不才是都已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說別人奇怪的人自己才是怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:19:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 有鯉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯉魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河裡 有很大一條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻我啊 想靠近看一看 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在樹根那裡 一搖一擺的 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你在撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一直…一直留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待…待在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去抓那條鯉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 這樣你會弄濕的 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 傻瓜仁碳 會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁碳


